Connection to Flavor:
"Santitas Cilantro Lime Tortilla embodies the vibrant culinary heritage that has thrived in Mexico and throughout South America for centuries.
Marking the celebration of Cinco de Mayo, which commemorates Mexico's victory at the Battle of Puebla. These Hint of Lime Tortilla chips capture the essence of Mexican tradition with a zesty twist.

chip_name: Lundberg Family Farms Organic Grounded Ancho Chile
description: In honor of Mexico's spirited celebration of independence on September 16th, our Lundberg Family Farms Organic Grounded Ancho Chile chips serve as a tribute to the rich cultural heritage.
